    Methods in org.mpris with parameters of type LoopStatus
    Modifier and Type
    Method
    Description
    void
    MPRIS.setLoopStatus(LoopStatus loopStatus)
    The current loop / repeat status May be: "None" if the playback will stop when there are no more tracks to play "Track" if the current track will start again from the begining once it has finished playing "Playlist" if the playback loops through a list of tracks If CanControl is false, attempting to set this property should have no effect and raise an error.
